War Evolved is a simple 2D tactical RPG

to compile it, you'll need autotools, make, g++ and SFML2+ (2.1)
run
> ./autogen.sh

if it works, the binary file (we) will be created


This project is under GPL license though uses PugiXML,
a XML file parser which is under Boost license
I have not written any code in src/pugixml folder
credits go to Arseny Kapoulkine (https://github.com/zeux/pugixml)

If you haven't downloaded War Evolved on google code,
you still can find it there https://code.google.com/p/warevolved/
to make sure you have the latest version


War Evolved is still under developpement (and not yet designed to be played)
but please repport any bug, feature request, ...


Have Fun and Thank You for downloading / playing
